        <div class=3D"body">
          <p>I was able to isolate the problem with the millisecond timesta=
mps. If you specify a timestamp you definitely get microsecond precision ba=
ck from =E2=80=9Cwritetime()=E2=80=9D, so I am pretty sure the problem is w=
