          <p>Looks like DataStax recently published a blog post on their te=
st results with Jepsen <a href=3D"http://www.datastax.com/dev/blog/testing-=
apache-cassandra-with-jepsen" rel=3D"nofollow">http://www.datastax.com/dev/=
