to suggest all of the issues identified here were resolved as of Cassandra =
2.1 and 2.2: =E2=80=9CWe did not identify any new issues in the 2.1 or 2.2 =
versions of Cassandra as a result of Jepsen testing. We still found great v=
alue in this test coverage, as it further reinforced our confidence in the =
